1.plot: Award-winning pop singer/songwriter Andrea Desmond is interviewed by episode host RJ Tolson before they play the What if challenge.

2.title: #PridePanel (Conner Jones/Joe Rissacher, Hadrian Panaroma, Lewis E. Woods)

episode of.title: RJ Tolson's Up and Coming (TV Series 2018– )

2.plot: It's Pride Month, and to honor it, a panel with members of the LGBTQ community have been assembled with episode host, Conner Jones.

imdb.plot outline: RJ Tolson's team conducts insightful, quirky, and inspiring interviews with people who haven't been content with just grazing through life - instead these up and comers are trailblazing as Entrepreneurs, Singers, Professionals, Actors, Influencers, Inventors, Creators and more. With rotating hosts for every episode, guests will talk about their journey and address issues - sometimes light, often times deep. Finally, the guests and hosts engage in epic challenges - this isn't for a boring Joe.
